{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Nova AI</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0a2a5c;\n            --secondary-blue: #3b5998;\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --background-color: #121212;\n            --accent-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .hero-shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero-shapes div {\n            position: absolute;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            opacity: 0.3;\n            animation: float 15s ease-in-out infinite;\n        }\n\n        .hero-shapes div:nth-child(1) {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            top: 10%;\n            left: 10%;\n            animation-delay: -2s;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n        }\n\n        .hero-shapes div:nth-child(2) {\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 150px;\n            bottom: 20%;\n            right: 15%;\n            animation-delay: -4s;\n        }\n\n        .hero-shapes div:nth-child(3) {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            top: 40%;\n            left: 50%;\n            animation-delay: -6s;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }\n            50% { transform: translateY(-30px); }\n            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            position: relative;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n        }\n\n        .features, .about, .contact {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: rgba(40, 40, 40, 0.5);\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 42, 92, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(10, 42, 92, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(10, 42, 92, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 40px auto 0;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.7);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border-color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Font Awesome Integration (for icons) */\n        @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"hero-shapes\">\n            <div></div>\n            <div></div>\n            <div></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>NOVA AI</h1>\n            <p>Intelligent Solutions for a Brighter Future</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>Nova AI is at the forefront of artificial intelligence innovation, dedicated to creating powerful, intuitive, and ethical AI solutions. We leverage cutting-edge research and development to empower businesses and individuals with the tools to solve complex challenges and unlock new possibilities.</p>\n                <p>Our mission is to democratize AI, making its transformative potential accessible and beneficial for everyone. We believe in a future where AI augments human capabilities, driving progress and fostering creativity.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Innovations</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                    <h3>Machine Learning</h3>\n                    <p>Advanced algorithms for predictive analysis and intelligent automation.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-cogs\"></i>\n                    <h3>Natural Language Processing</h3>\n                    <p>Enabling seamless communication between humans and machines.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Data Science</h3>\n                    <p>Extracting meaningful insights from vast datasets.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>AI Consulting</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored strategies to integrate AI into your business.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 Nova AI. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Crafted with <i class=\"fas fa-heart\" style=\"color: var(--brand-blue);\"></i> and innovation.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}